        <h1> Over 25 years experience in the design and production of displays</h1>
        
       <p><span class="blue">Tube &amp; Wire Display Limited specialise in manufacturing points of sale display stands and display racks primarily in tubular steel sections and mild steel wire. With a wealth of experience gained over our 30 years in business, we are one of the leading designers and manufacturers of Display Stands in the UK and we have extensive expertise in the retail sector.</span></p>

<p>At <span class="blue">Tube &amp; Wire Display</span>, we offer tailor made display solutions designed and manufactured at our on site 30,000 sq. factory based in Ashton-under-Lyne near Manchester. From design concept stage, producing initial samples through to the final production run with branded graphics, we offer the complete service. <span class="blue">Tube &amp; Wire Display </span> offer cost effective display solutions that deliver on promotional impact.</p>

<p>Whilst most of our work is made to order, we hold some standard display products in stock. Whether your requirement is for bespoke display products or standard stock products, we will be delighted to discuss your exact needs with you.</p>
        
